attributes.BoundText: We are an Island-wide environmental advocate.
attributes.RegColl:
Natural Resources Protective Association
North Shore Waterfront Conservancy
Community Boards 1, 2, & 3
The Greenbelt Conservancy
attributes.Knowledge:
NYSDEC
The Trust for Public Land
New York Audubon
attributes.Goals: Our goal is to increase the  number of  residents that  are knowledgeable about and who will advocate for conserving  open space, especially natural areas, on Staten Island.
attributes.Metrics: We track the number of volunteers and time devoted to our monthly Forest Restoration Workshops, and whatever metrics are pertinent to a specific grant.
attributes.Serv_Other: WE are occasionally involved in aiding or providing technical assistance to groups organizing  to preserve or improve open space, but that involvement is not a primary aim of the organization.
